    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_6_2167-2218",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2167-2218",
      "markText": "我渐渐明白，世间最可厌恶的事莫如一张生气的脸；世间最下流的事莫如把生气的脸摆给旁人看。这比打骂还难受。",
      "totalCount": 2325,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2167&rangeEnd=2218",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2167&rangeEnd=2218"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_4_2493-2528",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2493-2528",
      "markText": "我将于茫茫人海中访我唯一灵魂之伴侣，得之，我幸；不得，我命，如此而已。",
      "totalCount": 2214,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2493&rangeEnd=2528",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2493&rangeEnd=2528"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_5_907-988",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "907-988",
      "markText": "他死后，大家都很称赞差不多先生样样事情看得破，想得通；大家都说他一生不肯认真，不肯算账，不肯计较，真是一位有德行的人。于是大家给他取个死后的法号，叫他作圆通大师。",
      "totalCount": 1854,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=907&rangeEnd=988",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=907&rangeEnd=988"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_12_4162-4208",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "4162-4208",
      "markText": "社会所需要的是做事的人才，学堂所造成的是不会做事又不肯做事的人才，这种教育不是亡国的教育吗？",
      "totalCount": 1819,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=4162&rangeEnd=4208",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=4162&rangeEnd=4208"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_1_416-452",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "416-452",
      "markText": "人生意义就在我们怎样看人生。意义的大小浅深，全在我们怎样去用两手和脑部。",
      "totalCount": 1806,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=416&rangeEnd=452",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=416&rangeEnd=452"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_17_494-587",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "494-587",
      "markText": "凡富于创造性的人必敏于模仿，凡不善模仿的人决不能创造。创造是一个最误人的名词，其实创造只是模仿到十足时的一点点新花样。古人说得最好：“太阳之下，没有新的东西。”一切所谓创造都从模仿出来。",
      "totalCount": 1547,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=494&rangeEnd=587",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=494&rangeEnd=587"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_2_32-44",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "32-44",
      "markText": "新生活就是有意思的生活。",
      "totalCount": 1386,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=32&rangeEnd=44",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=32&rangeEnd=44"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_8_95-119",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "95-119",
      "markText": "他说，“我年纪越大，越感觉到容忍比自由更重要”。",
      "totalCount": 1360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=95&rangeEnd=119",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=95&rangeEnd=119"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_2_981-1034",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "981-1034",
      "markText": "为什么这个？为什么那个？——你试办一两天，你就会觉得这三个字的趣味真是无穷无尽，这三个字的功用也无穷无尽。",
      "totalCount": 1190,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=981&rangeEnd=1034",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=981&rangeEnd=1034"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_14_293-347",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "293-347",
      "markText": "生命本没有意义，你要能给它什么意义，它就有什么意义。与其终日冥想人生有何意义，不如试用此生做点有意义的事……",
      "totalCount": 1160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=293&rangeEnd=347",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=293&rangeEnd=347"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_12_2529-2617",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "2529-2617",
      "markText": "我回中国所见的怪现状，最普通的是“时间不值钱”。中国人吃了饭没有事做，不是打麻雀，便是打“扑克”。有的人走上茶馆，泡了一碗茶，便是一天了。有的人拿一只鸟儿到处逛逛，也是一天了。",
      "totalCount": 1131,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2529&rangeEnd=2617",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2529&rangeEnd=2617"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_8_1835-1926",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1835-1926",
      "markText": "一切对异端的迫害，一切对“异己”的摧残，一切宗教自由的禁止，一切思想言论的被压迫，都由于这一点深信自己是不会错的心理。因为深信自己是不会错的，所以不能容忍任何和自己不同的思想信仰了。",
      "totalCount": 1078,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1835&rangeEnd=1926",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1835&rangeEnd=1926"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_2_734-768",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "734-768",
      "markText": "我为什么要干这个？为什么不干那个？回答得出，方才可算是一个人的生活。",
      "totalCount": 972,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=734&rangeEnd=768",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=734&rangeEnd=768"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_3_1302-1344",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1302-1344",
      "markText": "我怕的是一般根底浅薄的青年，动辄抄袭名人一两句话，敢于扯起幌子，便“肆无忌惮”起来。",
      "totalCount": 960,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1302&rangeEnd=1344",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1302&rangeEnd=1344"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_14_459-519",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "459-519",
      "markText": "人生固然不过一梦，但一生只有这一场做梦的机会，岂可不努力做一个轰轰烈烈像个样子的梦？岂可糊糊涂涂懵懵懂懂混过这几十年吗？",
      "totalCount": 936,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=459&rangeEnd=519",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=459&rangeEnd=519"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_1_1790-1816",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1790-1816",
      "markText": "不要丢掉这梦，要好好去做！即算是唱戏，也要好好去唱。",
      "totalCount": 900,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40133513&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1790&rangeEnd=1816",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27132be072646389271cd35?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1790&rangeEnd=1816"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40133513_15_3518-3581",
